Package: rfutbin
Type: Package
Title: Search prices for FIFA Ultimate Team players in Futbin webpage
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Redondo-Sanchez", email = "danielredondosanchez@hotmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Daniel Redondo SÃ¡nchez <danielredondosanchez@hotmail.com>
Description: This package provides an R interface to Futbin,
    obtaining the live prices of FIFA Ultimate Team players, as well as
    other interesting information (stats, version and positions, popularity, ...).
    It also provides an interactive radar plot to easily visualize the main stats
    of the players: pace, shooting, dribbling, defense and physical.
